==English==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/pəˈteɪtəʊ/}}
*{{audio|en-us-potato.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-eɪtəʊ|-eɪtəʊ]]

===Etymology===
From Taino [[batata]] ([[sweet potato]]) via Spanish [[patata]] (not from a hypothetical Nahuatl "potatl").

===Noun===
'''potato''' (''plural:'' '''[[potatoes]]''')

#A plant [[tuber]], ''[[Solanum tuberosum]]'', often eaten as a starchy vegetable, particularly in the [[Americas]] and [[Europe]]. 

====Derived terms====
*[[couch potato]]

